{
  "texts": [
    "The idea is to reason with the system and pursue it to change the decision if needed.",
    "For example, if any recommendation is unclear or unexpected, they want the opportunity to inform and reason with the system.",
    "In a more explicit sense, they would like to have an argumentative discussion.",
    "As a participant described, If I receive any recommendation that does not match my interest, I think I should be able to talk to the system as humans do with another.",
    "I can engage in conversation, give feedback and the system can change the type of content it recommends me in future."
  ]
}